#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:2
msgid "XSS保护"
msgstr "XSS Protection"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:5
msgid "HTML过滤"
msgstr "HTML Filtering"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:6
msgid "使用一些白名单或者黑名单来过滤用户输入的HTML，以实现过滤的效果。例如DOMPurify等工具都是用该方式实现了XSS的保护。"
msgstr ""
"Use allowlists or blocklists to filter user-supplied HTML. Tools such as "
"DOMPurify implement XSS protection in this way."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:9
msgid "X-Frame"
msgstr "X-Frame"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:10
msgid "X-Frame-Options 响应头有三个可选的值："
msgstr "The X-Frame-Options response header has three optional values:"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:12
msgid "DENY"
msgstr "DENY"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:13
msgid "页面不能被嵌入到任何iframe或frame中"
msgstr "The page cannot be embedded in any iframe or frame"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:14
msgid "SAMEORIGIN"
msgstr "SAMEORIGIN"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:15
msgid "页面只能被本站页面嵌入到iframe或者frame中"
msgstr "The page can only be embedded in an iframe or frame by pages from the same site"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:16
msgid "ALLOW-FROM"
msgstr "ALLOW-FROM"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:17
msgid "页面允许frame或frame加载"
msgstr "The page allows loading by a frame or iframe"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:20
msgid "XSS保护头"
msgstr "XSS Protection Header"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:21
msgid ""
"基于 Webkit 内核的浏览器(比如Chrome)在特定版本范围内有一个名为XSS "
"auditor的防护机制，如果浏览器检测到了含有恶意代码的输入被呈现在HTML文档中，那么这段呈现的恶意代码要么被删除，要么被转义，恶意代码不会被正常的渲染出来。"
msgstr ""
"WebKit-based browsers, such as Chrome, had a protection mechanism called "
"XSS Auditor in certain version ranges. If the browser detected input "
"containing malicious code being reflected in an HTML document, the "
"rendered malicious code would either be removed or escaped, preventing it "
"from being rendered normally."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:23
msgid "而浏览器是否要拦截这段恶意代码取决于浏览器的XSS防护设置。"
msgstr "Whether the browser blocks this malicious code depends on the browser's XSS protection settings."

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:25
msgid "要设置浏览器的防护机制，则可使用X-XSS-Protection字段 该字段有三个可选的值"
msgstr "The browser protection mechanism can be configured with the X-XSS-Protection header. This header has three optional values"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:28
msgid "``0`` : 表示关闭浏览器的XSS防护机制"
msgstr "``0``: disables the browser's XSS protection mechanism"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:29
msgid ""
"``1`` : 删除检测到的恶意代码， 如果响应报文中没有看到 X-XSS-Protection 字段，那么浏览器就认为X-XSS-"
"Protection配置为1，这是浏览器的默认设置"
msgstr ""
"``1``: removes detected malicious code. If the X-XSS-Protection header is "
"not present in the response, the browser treats X-XSS-Protection as being "
"configured to 1, which is the browser's default setting"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:30
msgid "``1; mode=block`` : 如果检测到恶意代码，在不渲染恶意代码"
msgstr "``1; mode=block``: if malicious code is detected, the page is blocked instead of rendering the malicious code"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/mitigation.rst:32
msgid "FireFox没有相关的保护机制，如果需要保护，可使用NoScript等相关插件。"
msgstr "Firefox does not have a related protection mechanism. If protection is needed, plugins such as NoScript can be used."
